urvival strategy.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714970/extras/4198958e54dbc90e3133abdf9a2083ed.poster.avif?t=1768835096\" width=1170 height=638 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714970/extras/4198958e54dbc90e3133abdf9a2083ed.webm?t=1768835096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714970/extras/4198958e54dbc90e3133abdf9a2083ed.mp4?t=1768835096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714970/extras/8461e8e1d1283db40580c1fbe57496d7.avif?t=1768835096\" width=780 height=117 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your survival hinges on collaboration. You cannot make it alone. Use proximity voice chat to share discoveries, warn teammates of lurking dangers, and plan your next move in real-time. Work as a unit to lure entities into traps or solve environmental puzzles. Whether you are baiting the Smiler or watching your friend's back in the dark, every role matters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714970/extras/8fd24c65c35071c66f0a24697d2b2923.poster.avif?t=1768835096\" width=1170 height=638 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714970/extras/8fd24c65c35071c66f0a24697d2b2923.webm?t=1768835096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714970/extras/8fd24c65c35071c66f0a24697d2b2923.mp4?t=1768835096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >